Pick up the knife from the cabinet.
Turn right, head through the door and take left towards the potato in the kitchen.
Cut the potato with knife.
Turn around and move towards the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.

open the fridge,place the potato inside for some time and take it out and close the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and get in front of a dresser in the upper right corner.
Pick up the knife from the nightstand.
Get out of the room through an exit on the other side of the room, turn left and continue straight to a kitchen corner where you can see a pan and a plate and a potato in between.
Cut the potato with the knife.
Move to the sink on your right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the sliced fruit on the countertop.
Pick up a potato slice from the counter.
Now move to a fridge on your left.
Put the potato slice in the fridge, let it cool, then take it out.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled potato slice in the SinkBasin.
